lead_paragraph: We have Astoria dates to the 27th Sept. Mrs. ELIZA BETH GAINES, wife Of JOHN P. GAINESS, Governor of Oregon, met with her death from accidental causes on the 13th August. The Governor was on his way to Clotsop, where he had purchased a farm, to which he was removing his family.
